{"tid":1878464,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"不滿畀人唱 中三生迫兩師弟互相口交 拍片恐嚇掟上網","createTime":"2020-02-13T15:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T05:14:36.000Z","uid":132587,"like":16,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e8911c19c0672a84a574676599911fee448977","tid":1878464,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:27:38.000Z","msg":"【童黨欺凌】不滿畀人唱 中三生迫兩師弟口交 拍片恐嚇掟上網<br />\n2020-02-13 23:12<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4002860/org/c07ab2cdc1f741c985cf327d6f649c11.jpeg/JRDrtcM982qAJGjyH7tHlyvoPSBAnEJrw2N7mMNje5g?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4002860%2Forg%2Fc07ab2cdc1f741c985cf327d6f649c11.jpeg%2FJRDrtcM982qAJGjyH7tHlyvoPSBAnEJrw2N7mMNje5g%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=3c2e4366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍田發生駭人聽聞童黨欺凌事件，兩名中三男生疑不滿遭兩名中二同校師弟「講壞話」，相約對方「講數」，並找來最少6名同黨，自稱黑幫新義安成員，對師弟拳打腳踢之餘，竟迫他們互相口交，同時拍下淫片威脅擺上網，不准2人報警。惟終因家人發現事主身上傷痕，令童黨惡行敗露。<br />\n<br />\n事主被迫拍口交及拍片<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，兩名15歲主犯與兩名14歲事主就讀秀茂坪一中學。兩主犯疑不滿遭兩師弟「講壞話」，於是相約2月1日晚上到啟田商場「講數」，並「吹雞」找來6名男同黨，一行8人先後毆打兩事主，再迫令2人互相口交，更拍下口交片段，威脅他們不准報警及外揚事件，否則將口交片於網上公開，其間有人自稱黑幫新義安成員。<br />\n<br />\n兩事主受驚原不敢告知他人，但被家人發現身上傷痕，細問下揭發事件，家人大怒報警。<br />\n<br />\n5童黨被捕3人在逃<br />\n<br />\n觀塘警區反三合會行動組（反黑組）人員調查後，昨日（12日）在康田苑拘捕兩名主犯，並在單位內檢獲41克可卡因，市值約4.4萬元。警方隨後在平田邨拘捕另一名15歳同黨，他為雙失少年，同時是毒品提供者。3人涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害、以威脅促致他人作非法的性行為、自稱三合會成員、刑事恐嚇及販毒。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後再於康田苑附近拘捕2名14及15歲同黨，他們均為學生，涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害及以威脅促致他人作非法的性行為。此外，警方正追緝另外3名疑犯。"},{"pid":"6f84a80b4fb5ecdaa525ead1496fbbaf52352280","tid":1878464,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"好想被迫幫佢口交<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54413dfe1686f323c1934be972bcf4182d52ebed","tid":1878464,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6f84a80b4fb5ecdaa525ead1496fbbaf52352280","tid":1878464,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":20,"score":-17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"好想被迫幫佢口交<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"想睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1280a7fba1c23d55adfdafc359c871a196e4904","tid":1878464,"uid":88167,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:33:17.000Z","msg":"係咪即係69<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac9f6b0a36a24e8dfefaf79fb9286bbfb0553fc","tid":1878464,"uid":340244,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"好仆街 兩個男仔一世有陰影"},{"pid":"8065b4c6c6560dec11c008fefe5764da8746e00a","tid":1878464,"uid":340244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:34:02.000Z","msg":"變無性戀"},{"pid":"bb13fde25b033a70e135d5f92332c589a62d380d","tid":1878464,"uid":132587,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"1ac9f6b0a36a24e8dfefaf79fb9286bbfb0553fc","tid":1878464,"uid":340244,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"好仆街 兩個男仔一世有陰影"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 希望佢地本身鐘意男架啦"},{"pid":"23fb67d9e549b7c4b2dc8a74f3103603e8a7bd9c","tid":1878464,"uid":266672,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"係咪高雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a909ed6c0bb814896ef35ad0c816957e95678f","tid":1878464,"uid":48222,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />施暴者是咪上太多連登"},{"pid":"d745963750be17521b895aa722a133fbad77f5c6","tid"